{
  "stem": "14292.3",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- so-- and then I finally get home.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my mother was at home.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And Anna was home.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they knew I'm coming, because I send some messages for them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So that's the way I get home.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, my father wasn't there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I heard that he was taken away.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I-- one day, I get a-- my mother come from a shop and said that my father sent a message that he is in Germany, and he needs some help to get a car to pick him up.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was emotionally burned out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I-- but I said to my mother, this is not true.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My father is not in Germany, because if he would be, he would send you some note.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because I did some-- send some notes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so I told her not to do this, which was, of course, very hard for her.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And one day, she goes to her hairdresser, and there was a new hairdresser.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "In that time, everybody was talking about, you know, episode-- what happen in the war.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And-- you'll be-- and she-- this girl told my mother that her sister was killed in one of these place, because one of the Nazi guard, Hungarian Nazi guard, fell in love with her.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And so my mother took out a picture of my father.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And she said, oh, this is Uncle Zoltan-- Zoly-- my father name.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I know him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He was killed and-- with starvation.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he was so liked, because he even then give his food away, that they buried him and his-- and her sister in a separate grave, and not in a common grave.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And eventually, we were able to find, through her, my father.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
